D I Reporting C Annually A frequency: T O How to use: This indicator is the total number of staff working on HIV based out of PEPFAR facility sites. This R includes staff engaged in community work, but who are supported and based out of a PEPFAR- S supported facility. This includes but is not limited to Community Health Workers (CHWs) engaged in outreach, ARV delivery, or working as Linkage Officers, Peer Navigators, or Adherence Group coordinators.
